info.desc: Here is the end of the hall leading to the Transportation & Safety Building.
info.instr: Starting on the second floor of the Graduate Hotel, make your way to north-most point on the west side of the building.
Going through you should be going through a glass walkway.
The end of this is Washington Avenue Parking Ramp in front of you, but left there's a long hallway.
Taking this you get to the second floor of the Transportation & Safety Building.
